# This directory will hold your application source code.
# The team-build skill's implementation agents (Phase 2) will populate this
# with backend services, frontend components, and shared libraries as you
# run /team-build commands.
#
# Organize as you see fit — common patterns:
#   src/
#     backend/        # Backend services, APIs, data layer
#     frontend/       # Frontend components, pages, state
#     shared/         # Cross-cutting types, utils, constants
